WEBVTT

00:02.246 --> 00:03.624
‐ Previously on "The Path"...

00:03.624 --> 00:05.335
‐
Best and final.

00:05.335 --> 00:07.047
‐ You're accusing Steven Meyer
of molesting you.

00:07.047 --> 00:08.968
‐ Yeah.
‐ What do you want?

00:08.968 --> 00:11.305
‐ I want to be out in front,
speaking for The Movement.

00:11.305 --> 00:12.892
Why are you meeting
with him?

00:12.892 --> 00:14.729
What are you hoping
to gain from this?

00:14.729 --> 00:16.274
‐ He won't stop following me
until I hear him out.

00:16.274 --> 00:17.735
I am praying for you every day.

00:17.735 --> 00:20.448
‐ I don't need your
fucking prayers.

00:20.448 --> 00:22.787
I left the diaper bag
in the diner.

00:22.787 --> 00:25.458
And my dad took it.
‐ We'll get a new one.

00:25.458 --> 00:27.087
‐ Musa's moved
all their stuff out.

00:27.087 --> 00:28.757
‐ It probably has nothing
to do with you.

00:28.757 --> 00:30.176
‐ Then why isn't he answering
any of my texts?

00:30.176 --> 00:31.680
‐ I don't know.
‐ Well, he hasn't

00:31.680 --> 00:33.474
reached out to you
at all, has he?

00:33.474 --> 00:35.186
‐ I believe in you.

00:35.186 --> 00:37.024
‐ You know, I'm just a vessel
for The Light.

00:37.024 --> 00:40.280
‐ You don't feel like
just a vessel for The Light.

00:40.280 --> 00:42.200
‐ I took the medicine
last night.

00:42.200 --> 00:45.415
I was on one path, and you were
on a different one.

00:45.415 --> 00:48.922
You weren't lost,
but you weren't coming back.

