‐ Mm‐hmm.

32:31.390 --> 32:33.728
‐ I was hoping
that you could illuminate.

32:33.728 --> 32:37.110
‐ Ah, well, that didn't
take very long, did it?

32:37.110 --> 32:39.030
‐ Excuse me?
‐ Yeah.

32:39.030 --> 32:41.619
You're, what, the leader
